  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "video",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " component allows the user to control playback and hear audio.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "On this page, you’ll learn how to add a video component.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "strong"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "media-3624927",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-a-Video-to-the-Header",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add a Video to the Header",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add a video to your article, you simply add a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "video",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " component to a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "components",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " array. Here, you’ll add a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "video",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " component to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "components",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " array in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "header",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " component.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Alternatively, to include a video that plays automatically as the header’s background, you can use a ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/VideoFill",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ". With a video fill, playback and audio are disabled, but the video can automatically loop. With a video fill, but not a ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "video",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " component, you can also use a scene to affect how the opening section or chapter, including the video, comes into view. See ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/adding-a-scene",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/setting-up-the-advanced-tutorials#Download-the-Article-Bundle-Examples",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", you downloaded a bundle called ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "News_Design_Tutorial_Advanced_Article_3",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " that contains a thumbnail image. Now, you’ll move that image into your working folder and use it as a thumbnail.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Move the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "video-still.jpg",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file from the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Desktop/News_Design_Tutorial_Advanced/News_Design_Tutorial_Advanced_Article_3",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " folder to the folder that contains your working ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In your working ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file, delete the first section, including its ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "components",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " array. The code you are deleting begins with the opening brace (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "{",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") before ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "\"role\": \"section\",",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and ends with a closing bracket, a closing brace, and a comma (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "]},",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ").",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Copy the example code ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/adding-a-video#Header-Component-Copy-This-Code",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Paste the code inside the top-level ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "components",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " array, after the opening  bracket (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "[",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ").",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Your code should look like the example code ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/adding-a-video#Header-Component-Result",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you make this change in your code, you can preview your working ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "article.json",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file in News Preview to see the video.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Header-Component-Copy-This-Code",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "Header Component: Copy This Code",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "    {",
            "      \"role\": \"header\",",
            "      \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "      \"behavior\": {",
            "        \"type\": \"parallax\",",
            "        \"factor\": 0.8",
            "      },",
            "      \"components\": [",
            "        {",
            "          \"role\": \"video\",",
            "          \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "          \"URL\": \"http://podcasts.apple.com/resources/462787156.mp4\",",
            "          \"stillURL\": \"bundle://video-still.jpg\",",
            "          \"accessibilityCaption\": \"Sed ut pers piciatis unde omnis iste natus volup tatem accusantium dolor emque, totam rem aperiam.\"",
            "        }",
            "      ]",
            "    },"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Header-Component-Result",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "Header Component: Result",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Ellipses (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "...",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") indicate lines of code that have been omitted from this example.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  ...",
            "  \"components\": [",
            "    {",
            "      \"role\": \"header\",",
            "      \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "      \"behavior\": {",
            "        \"type\": \"parallax\",",
            "        \"factor\": 0.8",
            "      },",
            "      \"components\": [",
            "        {",
            "          \"role\": \"video\",",
            "          \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "          \"URL\": \"http://podcasts.apple.com/resources/462787156.mp4\",",
            "          \"stillURL\": \"bundle://video-still.jpg\",",
            "          \"accessibilityCaption\": \"Sed ut pers piciatis unde omnis iste natus volup tatem accusantium dolor emque, totam rem aperiam.\"",
            "        }",
            "      ]",
            "    },",
            "    ...",
            "  ],",
            "  ...",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
